- Blocks:
  - Block 1: AI Analysis Engine and Health Scoring Engine foundations.
  - Block 2: Caching Layer integration and data access patterns.
  - Block 3: Report Editor components and Snapshot mechanism.
  - Block 4: PDF Export pipeline with server-side rendering and queuing.
  - Block 5: Notifications & In-app inbox integration.
  - Block 6: Export Settings UI and PDF template integration.
- Sequencing Rule:
  - Authentication and core data setup must be completed before dashboard/workspace/analytics pages when both exist.
  - Implement caching and health scoring before rendering the full Report Viewer to ensure snappy UX.

