### Validation
- Response shapes must be validated: const sections = Array.isArray(response?.sections) ? response.sections : [].
- For array-based data, guard all map/filter/reduce usages: (sections ?? []).map(...)
- Optional chaining for deeply nested API responses: data?.sections?.[0]?.content

