## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] The Report Viewer renders all sections with AI-generated content and supports inline edits with autosave and snapshot creation.
- [ ] Health Score Engine computes overall and sub-scores with correct weighting and optional benchmarking; results persist.
- [ ] AI Analysis Engine returns structured payloads for all sections with support for depth levels and optional benchmarks.
- [ ] PDF Export pipeline starts, processes in a queue if necessary, applies branding, and provides a downloadable URL; status updates are reflected in UI and notifications.
- [ ] Caching layer reduces API latency for repeated fetches within a session; invalidation occurs on edits/snapshots.
- [ ] Notifications system delivers in-app and email notifications for analysis completion, export readiness, and errors.
- [ ] All code adheres to the runtime safety rules: nullish coalescing for Supabase results, guarded array operations, proper useState defaults, validated API responses, optional chaining, and safe destructuring defaults.

